{% extends '_templates/base.njk' %}

{% block page_title %}Celeste Olivarez's Movies{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<div class="container">
  <div class="mt-5">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col">
      <h1>Why Are Movies so Important?</h1>
      <p>Movies have always been more than just entertainment for me. They’re a way to connect with emotion, memory and perspective. I love the feeling of getting lost in a story, of seeing the world through someone else’s eyes, even if just for a couple hours. Movies create moments that stick, and there’s something special about going out to watch them. Sitting in a dark theater, surrounded by strangers all experiencing the same thing at the same time is crucial to a movie experience. It’s a shared experience that reminds me why storytelling matters. In a world that moves fast, movies slow us down, pull us in, and invite us to feel something real.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-5">
    <h2 class="h4">Movie Theaters Around Austin</h2>
    <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-2 g-4 mt-3">
      {% for theater in theaters.theaters %}
      <div class="col">
        <div class="card h-100">
          <div class="row g-0 h-100">
            <div class="col-md-8">
              <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column h-100">
                <h5 class="card-title">{{ theater.theater_name }}</h5>
                <p class="card-text"><strong>Address:</strong> {{ theater.address }}</p>
                <p class="card-text"><strong>Rating:</strong> {{ theater.rating }}</p>
                <a href="{{ theater.source }}" target="_blank" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-primary mt-auto">Visit Website</a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4">
              <img src="/img/{{ theater.image }}" alt="{{ theater.theater_name }}" class="img-fluid rounded-end h-100 w-100" style="object-fit: cover;">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
{% endblock %}
